66
00:04:43,192 --> 00:04:46,092
Di punggung Tuan Hoya ada bekas luka kecil.

67
00:04:47,092 --> 00:04:49,892
Tuan Kusumoto dulu kurus ketika ia masih kecil

68
00:04:49,892 --> 00:04:52,892
