117
00:07:20,792 --> 00:07:25,192
-Siapa peduli? -Siapa peduli?

118
00:07:25,192 --> 00:07:27,092
Ini cukup penting, aku katakan.

119
00:07:27,092 --> 00:07:28,292
Aku mengerti.

120
00:07:28,292 --> 00:07:30,392
