178
00:10:10,992 --> 00:10:13,592
Gari karena dia adalah seorang kutu buku?

179
00:10:13,592 --> 00:10:14,992
Apa kau tahu?

180
00:10:14,992 --> 00:10:19,992
Ketika bocah itu makan mie goreng di rumah pantai,

181
00:10:19,992 --> 00:10:23,192
